    <title>Women and Girls contributor: Thomas Bwire</title>
    <description>Thomas Bwire is a journalist based in the Kibera slums, with a passion for telling development stories from the grassroots level. He is one of the cofounders and the editor of Habari Kibra, which trains Kibera teens to tell the narratives of the slums using analytical journalism. Follow him @thomasbwire and @HabariKibra.
</description>
